@dpsBase = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Consulta al grafo (POST /api/v1/graph/query)
POST {{dpsBase}}/graph/query
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "question": "¿Qué vecinos tiene la entidad Comando General de la Fuerza Aérea?",
  "max_results": 20,
  "chat_id": 1
}


### Sin chat_id (opcional)
POST {{dpsBase}}/graph/query
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "question": "Listá organizaciones relacionadas con aviación civil.",
  "max_results": 10
}
